3cdfc16efad","tid":1557934,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:15:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mme1QAAF9ms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMme1QAAF9ms&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=38406b3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mme1QAAF9ms</a><br />\n<br />\n原曲：高地大教堂 Highland Cathedral<br />\n填詞：Hans J&uuml;rgensmeyer<br />\n2019年版詞：法蘭西多士<br />\n演奏：黑暗超夢夢<br />\n演唱：自由香港合唱團<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n偉哉香港 我城我等家邦<br />\n傲覽碧海 彪炳戰績輝煌<br />\n仁義禮智 隨伴乘風破浪<br />\n垂範東方 履途挽手逕創<br />\n<br />\n念城邦 立憲遵治道<br />\n歐亞古禮 共冶一爐<br />\n效龍獅 尚智尊道義<br />\n矢勇矢德致志<br />\n<br />\n美哉香港 似洋紫荊茂盛<br />\n耀眼光彩 彰高貴顯尊榮<br />\n苗裔遍世 凝聚同心唱詠<br />\n樂禮鏗鏘 四鄰也當謁敬<br />\n<br />\n自由港 未怕海浩瀚<br />\n自強不朽 是我海岸<br />\n太平山 做我等助佑<br />\n敦我克己奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n勇武香港 眾民處變不驚<br />\n盡每分光 光顯社稷威名<br />\n無懼戰鬥 無懼捨生獻命<br />\n縱使犧牲 自由自可戰勝"},{"pid":"3a472df668a625fe6ef0104221c9f9cc0d46dc6a","tid":1557934,"uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94511a7fd1a38ffff1ffa7b5056dfde711b9546f","tid":1557934,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c48f3702b608f39c314155884792ed151ec3088","tid":1557934,"uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3353838b1fc8027dd048005415a5634ff1909d5c","tid":1557934,"uid":131125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:06:11.000Z","msg":"幾段係okay嘅<br />\n但第二段歌詞有啲字可唔可以加埋近音字括住<br />\n預見到到時現場見住啲人攞住張歌詞紙都唱唔出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"可以呀<br />\n<br />\n原post都有整咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:14:24.000Z","msg":"有無link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者可唔可以直接copy過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy